{"tid":463058,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(大時代）騰訊投資50個公司相繼進行IPO","createTime":"2017-11-09T06:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T06:51:46.000Z","uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67323bb2cc96c75437460cdb2d0504c5d15fd8b0","tid":463058,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:49:28.000Z","msg":"【逾千億美元投資不同企業】<br />\n【騰訊:專注投資消費互聯網】<br />\n<br />\n騰訊投資併購部總經理李朝暉表示，目前已投資超過 50 個公司規模在 10 億美元以上公司，當中有 15 個，今年就進行 IPO，未來會繼續推動公司上市，包括明年推動騰訊音樂上市。<br />\n<br />\n「閱文最近令整個香港市場上火爆的局面，可以證明公司的優質，以及我們為它們所帶來的賦能，給大家所創造巨大的價值。」<br />\n<br />\n作為下一個分拆對象，騰訊音樂表示，目前旗下主要業務包括 QQ 音樂及全民 K 歌，活躍用戶已經超過一億人。<br />\n<br />\n「已有 8 億注冊用戶，每天的播放量大概 2 億，用戶群以 18 到 24 歲年青為主。」<br />\n<br />\n騰訊稱投資團隊非常專注，繼投資 TESLA 後，日前又入股 SNAP 12% 股權。<br />\n<br />\n「我們投資的話，最核心的領域，其實就是消費互聯網。」<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n【增持 Snap 股權至12%】【騰訊:入股 Snapchat是策略投資】<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/D3vB9z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FD3vB9z&d=e%2B11qaBe0KYJzSebqjOx1TM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=e80cceb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/D3vB9z</a><br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#騰訊　#投資　#投資企業 #閱文　#創造價值　#騰訊音樂"},{"pid":"0fa24e6424f84563b8f1222bdc20111d31ce8bf3","tid":463058,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> in ten we cent"},{"pid":"ac38a8e0706d8574dc99b372b55be2fd025ba367","tid":463058,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> in ten we cent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那野個個連登仔9衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/